## What We're Building

**FitRealm** is a mobile RPG where real-world **movement of any kind** directly powers in-game survival and progression. Walking, running, cycling, hiking — any physical movement counts. The player owns a village anywhere on Earth — chosen freely at signup, not tied to their real location. The game world is layered over Mapbox as a custom fantasy-styled map overlay.

After any movement session (walk, run, cycle, hike, or indoor workout), the player banks those miles and then **chooses how to spend them**. **Miles are the universal currency of FitRealm.** Every resource in the game — Food, Medicine, Wood, Stone, map exploration, building construction — is ultimately purchased with miles. Movement is money. You decide how to invest it: feed your village today, or save up for a building that pays off next week? This creates meaningful strategic decisions after every workout.

This is **not** a fitness app with game rewards bolted on. The movement **is** the core mechanic. No activity = village eventually decays. Consistent activity = thriving, growing kingdom.

