### Ads (Phase 3 — Only With Real Users)
- **Rewarded video ads only**: "Watch a short video to earn 5 Gems" — always optional, player-initiated
- Appear as an option on the Gem spending screen: "Not enough gems? Watch a video for 5 free"
- **Never interrupt gameplay** with forced ads
- Supporter Pack holders and Realm Pass subscribers see no ad options at all
- Max 5 rewarded ads per day to prevent abuse

### Monetization Design Rules
- The game is FULLY playable for free. Every feature is accessible without paying.
- Paying speeds things up or adds convenience but NEVER gates content.
- Never sell resources directly (no "buy 50 Food for $0.99") — this would undermine the movement loop.
- Never sell miles or movement credit — this would destroy the core mechanic.
- Cosmetics from World Events are earn-only, never purchasable.
- The Supporter Pack exists so fans can say "I helped build this" — it should feel like patronage, not a paywall.

