## Analytics & Success Metrics

Track these from Day 1 to know if the game is working. Log events to Supabase (or a lightweight analytics service like PostHog free tier).

### North Star Metric
**Weekly Active Movers (WAM)**: unique users who logged at least one movement session in the last 7 days. This is the single metric that tells you if the core loop is working. Everything else is secondary.

### Key Metrics Dashboard

**Retention:**
| Metric | Target (healthy) | How to measure |
|---|---|---|
| Day 1 retention | >40% | Users who return the day after signup |
| Day 7 retention | >20% | Users who return 7 days after signup |
| Day 30 retention | >10% | Users who return 30 days after signup |
| Onboarding completion (Day 7 chain) | >60% | Users who finish all 7 onboarding quests |

**Engagement:**
| Metric | What it tells you |
|---|---|
| Avg miles/user/week | Is movement frequency healthy? |
| Avg allocations/user/day | Are players engaging with the resource system? |
| Quests completed/day | Are random quests compelling? |
| Rally rate | Is the social layer working? (Rallies given / faction events seen) |
| Faction join rate | % of users in a faction by Day 7 |
| Building construction rate | % of users who build first building by Day 14 |

**Monetization (Phase 1+):**
| Metric | What it tells you |
|---|---|
| Supporter Pack conversion | % of users who buy it (target: 2-5%) |
| Gem purchase rate | % of users who buy gems (target: 1-3%) |
| ARPU (avg revenue per user) | Revenue health |
| Gem earn/spend ratio | Is the gem economy balanced? (target: users spend 40-60% of earned gems) |

**Health signals (watch for problems):**
| Signal | Problem it indicates |
|---|---|
| Day 1 retention <30% | Onboarding is broken — players don't understand the loop |
| Avg miles/user declining week-over-week | Core movement motivation is failing |
| >50% of users never build a building | Building system is confusing or costs are too high |
| Rally rate <10% | Social features aren't visible or compelling enough |
| >30% of villages in Ruined state | Decay is too aggressive or comeback path is too hard |
| Manual entry >40% of all activities | Possible cheating problem or GPS tracking issues |

### Event Logging
Log these events to Supabase (table: `analytics_events`):
- `app_open`, `session_start`, `session_end`
- `movement_started`, `movement_completed` (with distance, type, source)
- `miles_allocated` (with allocation type, amount)
- `quest_generated`, `quest_completed`, `quest_expired`
- `building_built`, `building_upgraded`
- `streak_continued`, `streak_broken`
- `rally_given`, `rally_received`
- `faction_joined`, `faction_left`
- `gem_earned`, `gem_spent`, `gem_purchased`
- `supporter_pack_purchased`, `realm_pass_subscribed`
- `onboarding_step_completed` (with day number)
- `comeback_triggered`, `comeback_completed`
- `achievement_unlocked`

