**Step 7: Village Placement + Onboarding (Days 19–21)**
- [ ] Onboarding flow: name village → place on world map → first crisis event → first movement
- [ ] Avatar creation screen (simple: skin tone, hair, face, eyes, outfit)
- [ ] Avatar rendering from composable SVG layers

**Phase 0 is DONE when:** You can install the app **on both iOS and Android**, create a character, place a village, go for a walk, bank miles, allocate them to feed your village, watch the map reveal, and see your village decay if you stop moving. Test the full loop on a physical iPhone AND a physical Android device before moving to Phase 1.

